General Assembly House Joint
Resolution No. 17
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1216
Referred to Committee on JUDICIARY
Introduced by:
REP. STAFSTROM, 129th Dist.
SEN. WINFIELD, 10th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF THE HONORABLE
STUART D. ROSEN OF AVON TO BE A JUDGE OF THE SUPERIOR
COURT.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of the
2 Honorable Stuart D. Rosen of Avon to be a Judge of the Superior Court,
3 to serve for a term of eight years from May 3, 2026, is approved and
4 confirmed, and he is appointed a Judge of the Superior Court for said
5 term.
LCO No. 1216 1 of 1

